4 PART V. REQUIRED TRAINING FOR PROSECUTORS ON PROSECUTING HATE
5 CRIMES
6 SECTION 5.(a) G.S. 7A-413 is amended by adding a new subsection to read:
7 "(e) The Conference shall develop and provide training to prosecutors on how to prosecute
8 hate crimes. For purposes of this subsection, the term "hate crimes" means an offense punishable
9 under G.S. 14-3(c), 14-401.14, or 14-34.11."
10 SECTION 5.(b) This section becomes effective July 1, 2025.
